meta {
  name: Deactivate a trusted origin
  type: http
  seq: 7
}

post {
  url: {{orgUrl}}/api/v1/trustedOrigins/{{trustedOriginId}}/lifecycle/deactivate
  body: none
  auth: none
}

headers {
  Accept: application/json
  Authorization: SSWS {{apiKey}}
}

docs {
Deactivates a trusted origin. Sets the `status` to `INACTIVE`.

**Responses:**
- `200`: Success
- `403`: 
- `404`: 
- `429`:
